channel.description: Idk what to write here so Im just gonna copy and paste the soundcloud description lol. Hey guys! I originally approached Tornait and asked him if I could see a part of the song and somehow I ended up remixing it lol. If you don't already know who Tornait is you should. His stuff is always jazzy and always put me in a good mood and I guarantee it will to you aswell (Especially Cornbread, it's so catchy aaaaaaaa Am so glad I got to remix it ;P ). Also thanks for 150 followers I guess. https://soundcloud.com/dontpartywithguns/tornait-cornbread-dpwgs-buttery-remix ![Tornait - Cornbread (DPWG's Buttery Remix)|500x500](upload://15TKsedL2WDhWRzDYeHIB3qGMgx.jpg)
